    "bio": "I am an experienced Automation Builder with 3+ years of experience helping businesses and people mitigate repetitive manual tasks and increase their overall productivity. I build custom automation workflows based on your individual business processes, using tools such as n8n, Make, Zapier, Google Apps Script, Selenium, Beautiful Soup, Puppeteer, or any advanced Python libraries to suit your needs.\n\nYou can book me via Upwork link below.",
